<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WA Gateway - Otomatiskan Pesan WhatsApp Anda</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans">

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">WA Gateway</h1>
                </div>
                <!-- ================== LOGIKA TOMBOL BARU DI SINI ================== -->
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                        <!-- Jika pengguna sudah login -->
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-md">
                            Go to Dashboard
                        </a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <!-- Jika pengguna belum login -->
                        <a href="/auth/login" class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-md">
                            Login / Daftar
                        </a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
                <!-- ============================================================== -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
                <span class="block">Platform WhatsApp Gateway</span>
                <span class="block text-indigo-600">untuk Kebutuhan Otomasi Anda</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 max-w-md mx-auto text-base text-gray-500 sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl md:max-w-3xl">
                Hubungkan beberapa akun WhatsApp, kelola sesi Anda sendiri, dan integrasikan dengan mudah ke platform seperti n8n menggunakan API kami yang andal.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-5 max-w-md mx-auto sm:flex sm:justify-center md:mt-8">
                <div class="rounded-md shadow">
                     <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
                            Masuk ke Dashboard
                        </a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/auth/login" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
                            Mulai Sekarang
                        </a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <div class="mt-20">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="lg:text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Fitur Unggulan</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                        Semua yang Anda Butuhkan dalam Satu Platform
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-10">
                    <dl class="space-y-10 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <dt>
                                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /></svg>
                                </div>
                                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Platform Multi-Akun</p>
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                                Hubungkan dan kelola beberapa nomor WhatsApp sekaligus dari satu dashboard pribadi yang mudah digunakan.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative">
                            <dt>
                                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                                </div>
                                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Antrian Pesan Anti-Blokir</p>
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                                Sistem antrian cerdas kami mengirimkan pesan dengan jeda waktu acak untuk meniru perilaku manusia dan mengurangi risiko pemblokiran.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative">
                            <dt>
                                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
                                </div>
                                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">API & Webhook Fleksibel</p>
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                                Integrasikan dengan mudah ke n8n atau sistem Anda sendiri menggunakan API Key per sesi dan webhook yang andal.
                            </dd>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative">
                            <dt>
                                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-indigo-500 text-white">
                                    <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" /></svg>
                                </div>
                                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Konfigurasi Sesi Mandiri</p>
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                                Atur Webhook URL, API Key, batas ukuran file, dan tipe media yang diizinkan langsung dari dashboard pribadi Anda.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                    </dl>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white mt-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-base text-gray-400">&copy; 2025 WA Gateway. All rights reserved.</p>
                 <% if (locals.adminContactInfo) { %>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Butuh bantuan? Hubungi Admin: 
                    <% if (locals.adminContactInfo.includes('@')) { %>
                        <a href="mailto:<%= locals.adminContactInfo %>" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline"><%= locals.adminContactInfo %></a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <span class="font-medium"><%= locals.adminContactInfo %></span>
                    <% } %>
                    </p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

